flowchart TD
  Intake[Approval request enters pipeline] --> Route[Typed approval route]
  Route --> Brief[Approval pipeline brief]
  Brief --> Materialize[Candidate generation]
  Materialize --> Judge[Request-faithfulness judge]
  Judge -->|pass| Present[Approved artifact view]
  Judge -->|repairable| Refine[Patch current approval revision]
  Refine --> Materialize
  Present --> History[Approval pipeline history compare / restore]
  History --> Archive[Approved record for an approval pipeline]
